'''亞當·里彭'''（{{lang-en|Adam Rippon}}；{{bd|1989年|11月11日|catIdx=Rippon, Adam}}）是一位[[美國|美國]][[花樣滑冰|花樣滑冰]]運動員。他是2010年[[四大洲花樣滑冰錦標賽|四大洲花樣滑冰錦標賽]]的冠軍得主。在2012年和2015年他獲得了美國花樣滑冰冠軍的榮譽。他出生在[[賓西法尼亞州|賓西法尼亞州]]，是六人兄弟中的老大<ref name=ISU-0809>{{cite web |url= http://www.isuresults.com/bios/isufs00008908.htm |title= Adam RIPPON: 2008/2009 |publisher= International Skating Union |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20200701102413/http://www.isuresults.com/bios/isufs00008908.htm |archivedate= 2020-07-01 |accessdate= 2015-07-11 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。他于2015年公开自己的[[同性恋|同性恋]]性取向。2018年获得[[2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会|平昌冬奥会]]参赛资格，成为美国第一位公开[[出柜|出柜]]的同性恋冬奥会运动员。<ref>{{cite news|title=Adam Rippon Is U.S.'s First Openly Gay Man To Qualify For Winter Olympics|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/thetorch/2018/01/07/576359822/adam-rippon-is-u-s-s-first-openly-gay-man-to-qualify-for-winter-olympics|accessdate=2018-02-07|work=NPR.org|date=2018-01-07|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822141033/https://www.npr.org/sections/thetorch/2018/01/07/576359822/adam-rippon-is-u-s-s-first-openly-gay-man-to-qualify-for-winter-olympics|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Wong|first1=Curtis M.|title=Adam Rippon Will Be First Openly Gay U.S. Man To Compete In The Winter Olympics|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/adam-rippon-winter-olympics_us_5a53a64ee4b003133ecadc67|accessdate=2018-02-07|work=Huffington Post|date=2018-01-08|archive-date=2019-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190212084458/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/adam-rippon-winter-olympics_us_5a53a64ee4b003133ecadc67|dead-url=no}}</ref>

